; A carryable ~0.4 m power cube. Charge bars are built at runtime on the top face (each its own
; material). The Port socket is on the +Z face (+Z faces out, so a plug seats nose-first into it);
; the cube is the socket's mount_body, so a taut cable drags the cube by its port.

